data.description: Short Sale! Lender has authorized short sale and they have set price. TLC needed. This is a hard used rental that has potential.  A lot in cul de sac in a well established neighborhood. Close to Methodist University and 295 to make it easy to zip into Ft Liberty or hit the interstate and go where ever. House has four bedrooms, two and half baths, nice deck in the shaded backyard. Storage shed is powered. Come see this hidden gem that needs polished.
